The paper is about designing the structure of neural networks, which falls under the category of neural networks and machine learning. Therefore, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the performance of the proposed approach compared to hand-crafted neural networks, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning). The experiments are conducted on image datasets, indicating that it may also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision). The approach involves genetic algorithms, which suggests that it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) or cs.SY (Systems and Control).
